Sun Jun 28 2026 Ciro Iriarte <ciro.iriarte+software@gmail.com> - 0.12.0-1

- Snapshots and tags. Cluster-wide `pc snapshot list` and age-based
  `pc snapshot prune` (--older-than/--before, --dry-run, confirm-gated).
- First-class guest tagging: `pc vm|ct|guest tag` (list/add/rm/set/clear,
  digest-locked), a `pc tag` cluster group (list/add/rm/clear/rename/
  export/import), and a `--tag` filter on guest listings.
- Reads work on PVE and PDM; tag writes are PVE-only.

